{"title":"铁证罪案岂能翻","authors":["池北偶","朱根华"],"dates":[{"year":2000,"month":1,"day":20}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁证罪案岂能翻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"池北偶 诗  朱根华  画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南京屠城血案，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"实在惨绝人寰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"皇军挥舞屠刀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杀人好几十万。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地下尸骨累累，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血腥罪证如山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"判决载入史册，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁也无法推翻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却有一帮小丑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"居然鬼话连篇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妄图抹煞罪行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要为屠夫喊冤。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无异登山倒粪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"简直臭气熏天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此种丑恶表演，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"定招天怒人怨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甘为战犯戴孝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只能丢人现眼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"休得放肆猖狂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"须知众怒难犯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高山上倒粪桶———臭名远扬（附图片）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}